@startuml LoginFlow
title TIMELAPSE - Login Multi-Plataforma
actor User
participant App
participant Backend
participant EmailService

User -> App: Solicita Login (Email)
App -> Backend: POST /auth/magic-link {email}
alt Sucesso
    Backend -> EmailService: Enviar Token/Link
    EmailService -> User: Recebe Email
    User -> App: Insere Token ou Clica no Link
    App -> Backend: Validar Token
    Backend -> App: JWT + User Profile
    App -> User: Acesso Liberado
else Email não encontrado/Inválido
    Backend -> App: 404/422 Error
    App -> User: Exibe mensagem de erro
end
@enduml
